## Owner Earnings Formula
`OE = NetIncome + D&A - MaintCapex - ΔWorkingCapital - SBC_adjust + OneOffAdjustments`

## DCF Formula and Parameters
- Explicit forecast years: {{ explicit_years }}
- Discounting: `PV = Σ(FCF_t / (1+WACC)^t) + TV/(1+WACC)^N`
- Gordon Terminal Value: `TV = FCF_(N+1)/(WACC-g)`
- Alternate terminal method supported by interface: Exit Multiple.
- Boundary condition: `WACC > terminal_g` (validation error otherwise).

